<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to The New York Public Library!</title>
</head>
<style media="screen">
    html {
        font-family: sans-serif; /* 1 */
        line-height: 1.15; /* 2 */
        -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; /* 3 */
        -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; /* 3 */
    }

    body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol";
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 400;
    }

    .welcome {
        background-color: #BB1D12;
        color: #FFF;
        font-family: Georgia, "Hoefler Text", Utopia, "Liberation Serif", "Nimbus Roman No9 L Regular", Times, "Times New Roman", serif;
        padding: 1rem 0;
    }

    .welcome h1 {
        color: #FFF;
        font-weight: 100;
        margin-left: 7rem;
    }

    p {
        margin-left: 7rem;
        width: 50%;
    }

    div.footer {
        background-color: #54514a;
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: .85rem;
        min-height: 4.5rem;
        padding: 2rem 0;
        position: relative;
    }

</style>

<blockquote>
{# @var data \NYPL\HoldRequestResultConsumer\Model\DataModel\HoldEmailData #}
<div class="edd">
    <h1 class="edd">Document Delivery System</h1>
</div>

<p>Dear {{ data.patronName }},</p>
<p>The recent request you placed via our Catalog's "Request Material From Off-site Storage" form is in the process of being delivered to your selected viewing location.
</p>
    <p>You will receive an e-mail confirmation when your item has arrived and is ready for pick-up at your requested location; no appointment necessary. For estimated arrival dates, details about procedures and contact information, please read our Offsite Collections homepage:</p>

<blockquote><a href="http://www.nypl.org/help/get-what-you-need/access-offsite-collections">http://www.nypl.org/help/get-what-you-need/access-offsite-collections</a></blockquote>

    <p> We kindly ask that you wait to call or e-mail the appropriate division until the expected arrival date has passed with no confirmation sent to you.</p>
<p> Title: {{ data.title }}<br/>
    Author: {{ data.author }}<br/>
    Barcode: {{ data.barcode }}<br/>
    Pickup Location: {{ data.pickupLocation }}<br/>
    Chapter Title: {{ data.docDeliveryData.chapterTitle }}<br/>
    Issue: {{ data.docDeliveryData.issue }}<br/>
    Volume: {{ data.docDeliveryData.volume }}<br/>
    Start Page: {{ data.docDeliveryData.startPage }}<br/>
    End Page: {{ data.docDeliveryData.endPage }}</p>
</body>
</html>
